## Request for Proposal - Dump Truck Procurement

### Description

Parks Canada Agency (PC) is seeking a supplier for the supply and delivery of one (1) Dump Truck. The vehicle must meet specified requirements and be delivered to the Canada Maintenance Compound #1 in Jasper, Alberta.

### Solicitation Information

* **Tender Reference Number:** WS3814028266
* **Publication Date:** 2023-04-05
* **Tender Closing Date and Time:** 2023-04-20T14:00:00 (Eastern Daylight Time)
* **Paperless Tender Link:** [http://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/15912451?extsite=MTU5MTI0NTFfQU4wMTQ4NDA1MDk5Mg==](http://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/15912451?extsite=MTU5MTI0NTFfQU4wMTQ4NDA1MDk5Mg==)

### Procurement Details

* **Procurement Category:** Goods and Services
* **Procurement Method:** Competitive Open Tender
* **Trade Agreements:**
	+ Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement
	+ Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA)
	+ Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement
	+ Canada-Honduras Free Trade Agreement
	+ Canada-Chile Free Trade Agreement (CCFTA)
	+ Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
	+ Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (CPFTA)

### Evaluation Criteria

* **Lowest Price**

### Communication

For any inquiries or questions, please contact:

Wall, Ruwani (SPAC/PSPC)
ruwani.wall@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca

### Attachments

[None]
